model = an.Model()
model.add_array(
    """[
            {
                "key": "TestData",
                "type": "NurbsCurveGeometry2D",
                "degree": 1,
                "nb_poles": 2,
                "knots": [-1, 0, 1],
                "poles": [[-1, 0], [0, 0], [2, 0]]
            }
        ]"""
    )
curve = model.get(0).data
integration_points = an.integration_points(degree=2, curve=curve)
assert_array_almost_equal(integration_points, [(-0.788675, 0.5), (-0.211325,
    0.5), (0.211325, 1.0), (0.788675, 1.0)])
